text.section:
Subject to approval or disapproval under subsection (c) of this section, each workers' compensation rating organization shall file with the Commissioner:
workers' compensation rates and rating plans that are limited to provision for claim payment;
each workers' compensation policy form to be used by its members or subscribers;
the uniform classification;
the uniform experience rating plan and rules; and
any other information that the Commissioner requests and is otherwise entitled to receive under this subtitle.
